Available Tools: add_to_cart | remove_from_cart | update_quantity | get_cart | apply_coupon | checkout
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "product_id": "string", "quantity": "number", "coupon_code": "string" }
Response Schema: { "cart_id": "string", "items": [{ "product_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": "number", "price": "number" }], "total": "number" }
---
Question: Apply the welcome discount code WELCOME20 to my current cart.
Call: { "func_call": "apply_coupon", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "WELCOME20" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-8821", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-101", "name": "Wireless Headphones", "quantity": 1, "price": 79.99 }], "total": 63.99 }

Question: Try using the expired coupon code SUMMER2023 on my order.
Call: { "func_call": "apply_coupon", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "SUMMER2023" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-8821", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-101", "name": "Wireless Headphones", "quantity": 1, "price": 79.99 }], "total": 79.99 }

Question: Complete the checkout process for my current items.
Call: { "func_call": "checkout", "product_id": "", "quantity": 0, "coupon_code": "" }
Response: { "cart_id": "CART-8821", "items": [{ "product_id": "PROD-101", "name": "Wireless Headphones", "quantity": 1, "price": 79.99 }], "total": 79.99 }

